data.description: This property has just arrived on the market in the picturesque city of Covina. Situated in a highly desirable location, this home boasts unparalleled convenience with close proximity to schools, parks, and local markets. Featuring 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms, this residence offers comfortable living spaces for families of all sizes. The highlight of this home is its expansive backyard, providing a perfect canvas for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. With its prime location and appealing features, this property is poised to attract discerning buyers. Don't miss this opportunity; this home is sure to be snatched up quickly in this competitive market. Schedule your viewing today before it's gone!
